devdoc.details: A smart-contract which stores user's deposited collateral.

addCollateralBalance(address,uint256).details: Opterator collateral balance data. Only manager contract can modify database.

addNetBalance(address,uint256).details: The foundation operator want to add some coin to netbalance, which can increase the FPTCoin net worth.

params.amount: the amount of the settlement coin which the foundation operator want to transfer in this contract address.
params.settlement: the settlement coin address which the foundation operator want to transfer in this contract address.

addNetWorthBalance(address,int256).details: Opterator net worth balance data. Only manager contract can modify database.

addOperator(address).details: add a new operator by owner.

addTransactionFee(address,uint256,uint25.details: An interface for add transaction fee. Only manager contract can invoke this function.

params.collateral: collateral address, also is the coin for fee.
params.feeType: transaction fee type. see TransactionFee contract

addUserInputCollateral(address,address,u.details: Opterator user input collateral data. Only manager contract can modify database.

params.user: input user account which need add input collateral.

addUserPayingUsd(address,uint256).details: Opterator user paying data, priced in USD. Only manager contract can modify database.

params.user: input user account which need add paying amount.

addWhiteList(address).details: Implementation of add an eligible address into the whitelist.

calSharedPayment(address[]).details: Calculate the collateral pool shared worth. The foundation operator will invoke this function frequently

getCollateralAndPremiumBalances(address,.details: calculate user's input collateral balance and premium collateral balance.     Specially used for user's redeem collateral.

params.userTotalWorth: the user's total FPTCoin worth, priced in USD.

getRealBalance(address).details: Retrieve the balance of collateral, the auxiliary function for the total collateral calculation.

getUserInputCollateral(address,address).details: Retrieve user's amount of the specified collateral.

getUserPayingUsd(address).details: Retrieve user's cost of collateral, priced in USD.

getWhiteList().details: Implementation of getting the eligible whitelist.

isEligibleAddress(address).details: Implementation of testing whether the input address is eligible.

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

removeWhiteList(address).details: Implementation of revoke an invalid address from the whitelist.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.      * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setCollateralBalance(address,uint256).details: set collateral balance. Only manager contract can modify database.

setNetWorthBalance(address,int256).details: set net worth balance. Only manager contract can modify database.

setSharedPayment(address[],int256[],int2.details: Set the calculation results of the collateral pool shared worth. The foundation operator will invoke this function frequently

params.firstOption: The new first unexpired option's index.
params.sharedBalances: All unexpired options' shared balance distributed by time.

setTransactionFee(uint256,uint256,uint25.details: set the rate of trasaction fee.

params.denominator: thedenominator of transaction fee. transaction fee = numerator/denominator;

setUserInputCollateral(address,address,u.details: set user's collateral balance. Only manager contract can modify database.

setUserPayingUsd(address,uint256).details: set user paying data,priced in USD. Only manager contract can modify database.

subCollateralBalance(address,uint256).details: Substract collateral balance. Only manager contract can modify database.

subNetWorthBalance(address,int256).details: Substract net worth balance. Only manager contract can modify database.

subUserInputCollateral(address,address,u.details: Substract user's collateral balance. Only manager contract can modify database.

subUserPayingUsd(address,uint256).details: Substract user paying data,priced in USD. Only manager contract can modify database.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

transferPayback(address,address,uint256).details: Operation for transfer user's payback. Only manager contract can invoke this function.

transferPaybackAndFee(address,address,ui.details: Operation for transfer user's payback and deduct transaction fee. Only manager contract can invoke this function.

params.feeType: the transaction fee type. see transactionFee contract

transferPaybackBalances(address,uint256,.details: Operation for transfer user's payback and deduct transaction fee for multiple settlement Coin.      Specially used for redeem collateral.Only manager contract can invoke this function.

params.PremiumBalances: the premium collateral balance if redeem worth is exceeded user's input collateral.
params.colBalances: the Collateral balance based for user's input collateral.
params.redeemWorth: the redeem worth, priced in USD.
